name: tem coisa que você olha e ela te olha de volta
description: "there are some things that when you look at it, it looks back at you" is a photo-poem about the singularity of existence, to feel and be in the moment (wich has already passed), and how it remember us how small we are towards time, nature and universe. Im a brazilian woman artist, you can find me at instagram/twitter by @ocvvvlta!
